## Group Categories

A `Category` object has the following properties:

+ id - internal category ID
+ name - category display name

## Category [/category/{id}]

+ id (string, required)

### View Category [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "id": 1,
            "name": "Extra Items"
        }
